        jLabel3.setText("<html>Low-carb diets have been popular for decades — especially for weight loss.\nThere are several types of low-carb diets, but all involve limiting carb intake to 20–150 grams per day.\nThe primary aim of the diet is to force your body to use more fats for fuel instead of using carbs as a main source of energy.</html>");
